# shadcn/ui Component Usage

## Overview
This project uses shadcn/ui for ALL UI elements. No custom UI components are allowed.

## Installation

### Initialize shadcn/ui
If shadcn/ui is not yet initialized in the project, run:

```bash
npx shadcn@latest init
```

This will:
- Install necessary dependencies (tailwindcss, class-variance-authority, clsx, etc.)
- Create a `components.json` configuration file
- Set up the `src/components/ui/` directory structure
- Configure Tailwind CSS
- Create utility functions in `src/lib/utils.ts`

### Adding Components
To install a specific component (e.g., button), use:

```bash
npx shadcn@latest add button
```

Common components you may need:
